    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >泡之星球派对开启！3D世界的多人欢乐泡泡对战！（qq群：932464250）</h2>这是使用泡泡欢乐对战的多人联机3D世界，有超过30个带着各种技能的角色可以解锁，还有包含500多个自定义模块的关卡编辑器，让你可以制作属于自己的关卡，让其他玩家一起在你制作的关卡里欢乐合作和对决！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/a2fc6fe869633d1dad3993dc42901610.poster.avif?t=1629856274\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/a2fc6fe869633d1dad3993dc42901610.webm?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/a2fc6fe869633d1dad3993dc42901610.mp4?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/7dac45a7b61b8792d53aed74958ae59e.poster.avif?t=1629856274\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/7dac45a7b61b8792d53aed74958ae59e.webm?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/7dac45a7b61b8792d53aed74958ae59e.mp4?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内置关卡编辑器</h2>游戏中目前包含500多种不同的地形模块，几十种障碍、机关道具！以及多种功能模块！让你可以做出各种有趣的关卡，让其他玩家在你的关卡里欢乐联机！<br>后续会逐步增加更多的DIY模块，甚至会加入怪物，NPC等可以制作多人PVE故事剧情的模块<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/9a7c316e78cd9edc3990688ab8c39c8d.poster.avif?t=1629856274\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/9a7c316e78cd9edc3990688ab8c39c8d.webm?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/9a7c316e78cd9edc3990688ab8c39c8d.mp4?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/a651464fd4e3c1c5ed2d9abc8a317704.poster.avif?t=1629856274\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/a651464fd4e3c1c5ed2d9abc8a317704.webm?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/a651464fd4e3c1c5ed2d9abc8a317704.mp4?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3D世界的泡泡对战，多种联机比赛模式</h2>核心战斗方式是使用泡泡或技能互相对战，目前有4种不同的比赛模式，后续会逐步增加！     <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/f555caa3e4354cc103aa7bfdc8f95e57.poster.avif?t=1629856274\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/f555caa3e4354cc103aa7bfdc8f95e57.webm?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/f555caa3e4354cc103aa7bfdc8f95e57.mp4?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/651e09847211db93e38e463d31709d4f.poster.avif?t=1629856274\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/651e09847211db93e38e463d31709d4f.webm?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701450/extras/651e09847211db93e38e463d31709d4f.mp4?t=1629856274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br><strong>1.泡星争霸赛：将所有敌方全部击败即可获胜（吃鸡模式）<br>2.勇往直前：躲避各种机关障碍并前往终点，最先到达终点的队伍或玩家获胜！玩家可以自己制作各种跑酷地图和其他玩家一起游玩！<br>3.水果之争：玩家们疯狂夺取地图上的水果，抢到最多水果的玩家获胜。<br>4.泡星计时赛：规定时间内，尽可能的击败其他玩家，击杀数最高的队伍或玩家获胜！</strong><br>玩家可以自己制作任何模式的地图在网上和其他玩家联机游玩！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不同技能的角色选择</h2>目前已经包含了30多个不同的角色可以解锁选择，每个角色都自己的一个主动技能和被动技能<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种不同的泡泡</h2>可以解锁选择不同的泡泡组合角色参加派对！<br><br>目前属于测试版，按照规划，后续会加入更多的模式，角色和DIY内容，希望玩家可以给出各种建议，一起打造这个游戏，让它更有趣，可以自制更多的玩法！",
